                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13198034" author="jbellis" created="Wed, 1 Feb 2012 18:36:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I poked at this a bit and decided that replacing SDF w/ Calendar isn&apos;t quite as simple as a text substitution. &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13198194" author="dbrosius@apache.org" created="Wed, 1 Feb 2012 21:57:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;use thread local for holding SimpleDateFormat&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13198293" author="urandom" created="Wed, 1 Feb 2012 23:05:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;committed w/ minor changes (style and convention); thanks Dave!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
